  <div class="column side">
    <h2>Wombo Combo</h2>
    <p>Buying items seperatly is great, but buying two items and using them in succession can bring you far into the game.  For example, use a Lucky Egg and a Lure module or a Incense to boost the XP you get from all of the pokemon you catch.  You can also buy five egg incubators and one lucky egg, and when you hatch all of the eggs in your inventory, be sure to apply the lucky egg to see your XP level soar!</p>
    
  
